{"tid":1444042,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"發夢係深水埗現場前線，有啲野想講","createTime":"2019-08-11T11:10:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T12:02:34.000Z","uid":79178,"like":37,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"99f5610378a668346856b93c76d27b9186a49959","tid":1444042,"uid":79178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T11:10:33.000Z","msg":"啱先深水埗係放完彈即刻沖上黎拉人<br />\n仲要係連發8粒以上<br />\n本身係大家都食完彈退緊，但班狗突然沖上黎捉人<br />\n最後睇翻有幾位手足比人拉左<br />\n勸大家以後退真係要互相照應，唔好自己一條友走，拉埋自己其他人走<br />\n退嘅時候真係唔好太急，情況許可一齊叫1212咁退，好易受傷，有節奏咁走。比狗追另計<br />\n同時亦有位手足都有叫過前線退，勸大家唔好即屌係現場叫退嘅人，要聽清楚人地個重點點解要退，大家係自己人，態度好啲<br />\n真係唔好再不停守，要變通，打游擊<br />\n之前我開po屌過班叫走嘅人，但宜加情況真係唔同左"},{"pid":"b269260f50207e0c8c1e6813278ad718749faa1d","tid":1444042,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T11:12:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d92ec0c4ad67065122b93b3e7fa5b28566b80902","tid":1444042,"uid":79178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T11:12:42.000Z","msg":"自推一下"},{"pid":"09a82a0ee4df02e1655fbce8f732a733c8306df4","tid":1444042,"uid":296669,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T11:13:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7da384985280b0567251beb7ec75157eb3f979a6","tid":1444042,"uid":79178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T11:14:00.000Z","msg":"後悔宜加開po，出面仲打緊，係我食完彈冇跟，都係集中翻算"},{"pid":"75b908090ecd539682d5e973478e76ec702d6ca0","tid":1444042,"uid":174578,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T11:14:05.000Z","msg":"基本守得即係陣地戰=有肉搏戰準備。。。<br />\n如果無呢個準備快閃就好"},{"pid":"b85d1f8cf1ff7cebfe925cb55cc2d911db24b0cf","tid":1444042,"uid":59522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T11:14:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ae8084306925e9153a0f86efbc2b13bd75f1e305","tid":1444042,"uid":33868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTim